  mySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 97984018d026c4b43a58ddaf45a14f31, type: 3}
  OutcomeRef: 3
  myName: woodwinds
  myDescription: "Thoughtful, imaginative, and delightfully quirky; you have a way
    of seeing the world that feels enchanting. Balancing logic and emotion is a piece
    of cake for you. You might be quiet for a bit in a group discussion, but after
    that moment of consideration you will come out with solutions and insights no
    one else thought of. Not the loudest voice in the room, but when you do speak,
    you leave a subtle, refreshing impression that\u2019s unmistakably yours. Others
    often describe you as whimsical or unexpectedly wise, and you embody both naturally.
    In a familiar tune you represent that little jizz, that bit of sparkle that peaks
    curiosity and lures people in.  "
